The paper discusses the Spectre attacks, which are related to computer security (cs.CR). It also focuses on microarchitecture, which falls under computer architecture (cs.AR). The paper proposes a formal analysis approach to fix vulnerabilities, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also mentions pipelining and out-of-order execution, which are concepts related to programming languages (cs.PL). Finally, the paper discusses the need for hardware and software co-design, which falls under systems and control (cs.SY).
